            <div class='column full'>
                <h3>Why do we care about link building in the first place?</h3>
                <p style='max-width: none'>
                    Naturally obtaining popular and relevant sites to link to yours is one of the best ways to acquire a high ranking in online search
                    results. According to the leading SEO blog MOZ, "link building is among the top tasks required for search ranking and traffic success."
                    Gaining people who are writing about you to link to your site is extremely efficient and effective in building up your link profile.
                </p>
                <p style='max-width: none'>
                    Basically, the more links you get to your site, the higher it shows up in search results. On top of that, your referral traffic will
                    likely increase from people clicking through on the links!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

